name: Vanillaware style TI
description:
Style embedding trained on Vanillaware's art (also some art from "The Vagrant" videogame was used, because they have a very close style). Good for generating girls and fantasy stuff. Tested on UnstableInkDream model https://civitai.com/models/1540/unstableinkdream

P.S. a lot of pictures that were used for training are very ecchi, so often it generates half-naked women
